00:16:53.004 --> 00:16:56.384
problem. We're in Boston. Cambridge is right across the

280
00:16:56.424 --> 00:17:00.084
river. As soon as you get someone who's good as a research technician,

281
00:17:00.264 --> 00:17:00.664
the

