00:25:00.064 --> 00:25:03.904
So this is an active thing, and then you find out the vulnerabilities, and

417
00:25:03.984 --> 00:25:06.524
then the fun begins of beginning to work up a target.

418
00:25:08.104 --> 00:25:08.284
So,

419
00:25:09.244 --> 00:25:13.154
this is a story that we just published a couple of years ago now, led by

