00:25:20.964 --> 00:25:23.063
stay before going on to grad school.

423
00:25:23.604 --> 00:25:27.314
Came in, was really amazing, decided that

424
00:25:27.704 --> 00:25:31.204
as she picked grad school, she was going to pick the brand new St.

