00:26:34.844 --> 00:26:37.604
I guess it's 10 to the negative 22 over here.

443
00:26:38.844 --> 00:26:39.484
And so

444
00:26:40.884 --> 00:26:43.544
find it to be-- actually, there was two separate screens.

445
00:26:43.584 --> 00:26:47.404
This was the newest version of DepMap at that time, and this was the original

