00:27:23.844 --> 00:27:24.994
And so then the question,

457
00:27:25.824 --> 00:27:27.453
as we're thinking about this, why

458
00:27:28.284 --> 00:27:32.024
would a ubiquitin ligase adapter constitute a specific vulnerability in

459
00:27:32.044 --> 00:27:35.964
