00:28:44.464 --> 00:28:45.244
kill the cells.

480
00:28:47.444 --> 00:28:51.364
And so went forward then with asking, what is the effect of

481
00:28:51.404 --> 00:28:54.544
DCAF5 knockdown on SWI/SNF subunit abundance?

482
00:28:55.124 --> 00:28:58.804
And this was one of the few times in my life when I was really

