00:33:41.514 --> 00:33:44.674
together but just came out last week led by Hayden

564
00:33:44.714 --> 00:33:48.463
Malone, who also joined the lab as one of those

565
00:33:48.494 --> 00:33:50.114
research technician positions.

566
00:33:51.394 --> 00:33:54.014
While Hayden's here, I have to just brag about her a little bit.

567
00:33:54.114 --> 00:33:58.014
She grew up in rural Mississippi, went to high school, decided there wasn't much

