00:35:09.974 --> 00:35:13.824
was that FIP actually localizes to active promoters,

590
00:35:13.994 --> 00:35:17.594
H3K4 trimethyl, K27 acetyl, K14 acetyl,

591
00:35:18.614 --> 00:35:21.214
mostly absence of the polycomb silencing mark.

592
00:35:21.254 --> 00:35:25.164
And when she knocked down FIP in three different rhabdoid tumor cell lines, what

