00:36:25.894 --> 00:36:29.834
subunits of this complex, CHD4 most strongly, but also

611
00:36:29.914 --> 00:36:32.754
other subunits of the Nurd complex.

612
00:36:33.474 --> 00:36:34.674
When she took a look at what

613
00:36:35.654 --> 00:36:39.514
