00:37:40.238 --> 00:37:43.758
subunits, ATPase subunits, companies had developed degraders.

631
00:37:44.478 --> 00:37:47.578
And so here we degrade the ATPase subunits

632
00:37:47.898 --> 00:37:51.558
or overexpress FIP now in 293T cells.

633
00:37:52.218 --> 00:37:54.998
So overexpress, this is the abundance of NRD subunits.

634
00:37:55.058 --> 00:37:58.858
Overexpressing FIP does nothing. Degrading SwitchNIF does nothing.

635
00:37:58.878 --> 00:38:02.538
But when you degrade SwitchNIF and then overexpress FIP,

636
00:38:03.118 --> 00:38:06.598
now you really reveal the ability of FIP that is active in

637
00:38:06.618 --> 00:38:07.728
degrading NRD.

638
00:38:08.858 --> 00:38:12.818
Does this happen? Is it dependent in vivo? So we go in vivo.

639
00:38:13.418 --> 00:38:16.138
Now we see this is what happens with FIP intact.

640
00:38:16.178 --> 00:38:17.738
When we knock out FIP,

641
00:38:18.638 --> 00:38:22.578
we significantly prolong. We don't get the same DCAF5

