00:39:19.138 --> 00:39:22.878
And now as we go from the graduate school all the way through postdoc

659
00:39:22.918 --> 00:39:26.478
into current times, what we're really seeing is cancer

660
00:39:26.758 --> 00:39:30.318
very strongly being promoted by disruption of fundamental

661
00:39:30.398 --> 00:39:33.898
transcriptional control, disruption of lineage-specific

662
00:39:33.958 --> 00:39:37.568
transcription programs, and the therapeutic

663
00:39:37.638 --> 00:39:41.258
vulnerabilities that result have, in every case, been

