thousands of trainees,

722
00:43:07.498 --> 00:43:11.418
128 countries and territories represented globally,

723
00:43:11.998 --> 00:43:15.138
391 attendees per lecture this year.

724
00:43:15.658 --> 00:43:18.758
This has just been phenomenal. As I look about...

