00:44:11.030 --> 00:44:14.340
And then Damon Runyon called us when the Sohn Foundation had pulled out.

741
00:44:14.890 --> 00:44:18.239
We need pediatric-focused funding, and so we have picked that up, and that has

742
00:44:18.350 --> 00:44:19.710
