00:45:06.970 --> 00:45:10.510
lab, Eric Fisher's lab, the Broad Institute, and a number of people at St.

757
00:45:10.730 --> 00:45:12.970
Jude, and funding, and I'm happy to take questions.

758
00:45:19.130 --> 00:45:22.510
Thank you. We've kind of run out of our time, but we probably can do a couple of

