00:45:29.030 --> 00:45:31.970
If not, I have a final question for you.

762
00:45:32.000 --> 00:45:32.970
Great. Sorry, I went longer than I thought I would getting it all in.

763
00:45:33.010 --> 00:45:33.370
That's no,

764
00:45:34.290 --> 00:45:34.910
no worries.

765
00:45:36.190 --> 00:45:38.370
We're in challenging times right now.

766
00:45:39.110 --> 00:45:42.970
Science is facing a lot of challenges, and I wonder

