00:45:43.030 --> 00:45:46.870
what advice you're giving mentees about that right

768
00:45:46.910 --> 00:45:47.489
now.

769
00:45:47.530 --> 00:45:51.350
Yeah, it's a good question. I think about times come and go,

770
00:45:52.070 --> 00:45:54.990
and it's really hard to know. I think about this on the medical side.

771
00:45:55.050 --> 00:45:56.910
I just used as an example, nursing.

772
00:45:56.930 --> 00:46:00.730
There are some years where people have huge recruitment things going on and signing

773
00:46:00.750 --> 00:46:04.650
bonuses for nurses, and then there's some years that it's super hard to

774
00:46:04.690 --> 00:46:06.770
